attributes.action: Making Essex Marshes national park and creating Forest Biosphere on Onsea island
attributes.additional_details:
The aim of this petition is to ask the government to give the Essex Marshes a National Park and Planting forest on Osea Island  as new Biosphere reserve for exinct species like

European Bison
European Elk
European Tarpen Wild Horse
European lynx
European Beaver
European Ospray
European Red Squirrel
European Wolverine
